At VEG Neuendorf, 82.5 ha are planted with cereals, 48.72 ha with root crops, and 20.47 ha with lucerne. The root crop areas are to receive 34 kg of phosphoric pentoxide (P2O5) per hectare, the lucerne areas 20 kg, and the cereal areas 17.5 kg.

How many decitons of superphosphate are required if it contains 17.3 percent phosphoric pentoxide?

14. (i) Find the least non-negative residue of $2^{400}$ modulo 10;
(ii) Find the last two digits in the decimal representation of $2^{1000}$;
(iii) Find the last two digits in the decimal representation of $9^{9^{9}}$ and $9^{9^{9^{9}}}$;
(iv) Find the least non-negative residue of $\left(13481^{56}-77\right)^{28}$ when divided by 111;
(v) Find the least non-negative residue of $2^{s}$ modulo 10, where $s=2^{k}, k \geqslant 2$.

formal_statement:
import Mathlib

/- 14. (i) Find the least non-negative residue of $2^{400}$ modulo 10;
(ii) Find the last two digits in the decimal representation of $2^{1000}$;
(iii) Find the last two digits in the decimal representation of $9^{9^{9}}$ and $9^{9^{9^{9}}}$;
(iv) Find the least non-negative residue of $\left(13481^{56}-77\right)^{28}$ when divided by 111;
(v) Find the least non-negative residue of $2^{s}$ modulo 10, where $s=2^{k}, k \geqslant 2$. -/
theorem number_theory_6127 :
    2^400 % 10 = 6 ∧
    (2^1000) % 100 = 76 ∧
    (9^(9^(9^(9^9))) % 100 = 89 ∧
     9^(9^(9^9)) % 100 = 70) ∧
    ((13481^56 - 77)^28 % 111 = 70) ∧
    ∀ s ≥ 2, s = 2^k → 2^s % 10 = 6 := by

